Item: runed mithril warhammer
Coder: Igneous
Path name: /d/Shire/easroad/eastern/wep/warhammer.c
Skill/Stat enhancements: 5-15 STR increase depending on the INT
                         of the wielder.
Type: Club
    WC: 42,47
    Hands: LEFT
    Wield: None
Magic: 60, Enchantment
       20, Enhancement
Resistance: None
Specials: None
Location: ~Shire/eastroad/eastern/inn2.c by Khaaz
Notes:  Fairily hard club to get, created because of the lack of
good npcs in the game wielding nice clubs. A little welcoming
present to the Shire for the Angmar guild If they can get it ;-)
 
Item: Runed longsword
Coder: Finwe
Path name: /d/Shire/rivendell/wep/m_longsword.c
Skill/Stat enhancements: None
Type: Sword
    WC: 55,50
    Hands: ANY
    Wield: None
Magic: 80, Enchantment
Resistance: None
Specials: Allows players to know if evil players or npcs are nearby
Location: /d/Shire/rivendell/npc/elrond.c and glorfindel.c
Notes:  Not available to mortals. Evil aligned creatures cannot wield 
        sword.
 
