Item: Thin Wooden Quarterstaff
Coder: Jaypeg
Path name: /d/Shire/common/trollsh/weapon/oakstaff.c
Skill/Stat enhancements: None
Type: Polearm
    WC: 45,42
    Hands: BOTH
    Wield: None
Magic: 60, Enchantment
Resistance: None
Specials: Very light, increased hit/pen.
Location: /d/Shire/common/trollsh/npc/ruletroll.c
Notes:    Replaced the Cruel Black Halberd


Item: Corrupted Mithril Weapons
Coder: Finwe
Path name: /d/Shire/common/trollsh/weapon/gem_*.c
Skill/Stat enhancements: None
Type: Varies based on weapon
    WC: Varies based on gem inserted
    Hands: BOTH
    Wield: None
Magic: 75, Enchantment
Resistance: None
Specials: Increased hit/pen based on gem rarity
Location: /d/Shire/common/trollsh/npc/grothaur.c
Notes:    The rarer the gem inserted into the weapon, the higher the hit/pen, 
          ranging from 40/41 to 50/50. When no gem is in the weapon, then 
          the hit/pen is 35/35.

 
